sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: GetPersonalVision
    C->>A: GetPersonalVision()
    A->>PM: GetPersonalVision()
    PM->>PA: LoadVision()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(vision.json)
    PA-->>PM: *PersonalVision
    PM-->>A: *PersonalVision
    A-->>C: *PersonalVision (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: SavePersonalVision
    C->>A: SavePersonalVision(mission, vision)
    A->>PM: SavePersonalVision(mission, vision)
    PM->>PM: Set UpdatedAt = now()
    PM->>PA: SaveVision(*PersonalVision)
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(vision.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit("Update personal vision")
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: GetAllThemeProgress [computation only, no persistence]
    C->>A: GetAllThemeProgress()
    A->>PM: GetAllThemeProgress()
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PA-->>PM: []LifeTheme
    loop For each theme
        loop For each active objective (recursive)
            PM->>PM: computeObjectiveProgress()
            PM->>PM: computeKRProgress() for each active KR
        end
        PM->>PM: Average top-level objective progress
    end
    PM-->>A: []ThemeProgress
    A->>A: Convert to Wails DTOs
    A-->>C: []ThemeProgress (Wails DTO)
